instructions: Put the charger under the plate.
Put the napkin on the plate.
Put the dinner fork on the left side of the charger.
Put the salad fork on the left side of the dinner fork.
Put the dinner knife on the right side of the charger.
Put the tea spoon on the right side of the dinner knife.
Put the soup spoon on the right side of the tea spoon.
Put the water glass above and to the right of the charger.
Put the wine glass to the right of the water glass.
Put the wine glass above the tea spoon.
Put the coffee cup above and to the right of the soup spoon.
Put the bread plate top left above the dinner and dessert forks.
Put the butter knife on the bread plate in a horizontal direction.
Put the dessert fork to the left of the water glass.
Put the dessert fork above the dessert spoon.
